                    <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #f59e0b; margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 5px; line-height: 1.4;">
                        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" style="margin-top:1px; flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
                        <span><strong>注意：</strong>若该款式为多件套且您仅需其中单件（如仅要上衣或仅要底裤），请务必在下方明确说明。</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <label style="display:block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #334155; margin-bottom: 8px;">定制需求描述</label>
                    <textarea id="customRemark" placeholder="请详细描述您的轻定制需求。&#10;例如：肩带加宽至2cm、使用zigzag边缘工艺等..." spellcheck="false" style="flex: 1; min-height: 120px; margin-bottom: 20px;"></textarea>
                    
                    <label style="display:block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #334155; margin-bottom: 8px;">参考附件</label>
                    <div class="premium-upload-row" id="customDropzone" onclick="document.getElementById('customFile').click()" style="padding: 12px 15px;">
                        <div class="upload-label-group">
                            <span class="upload-label-main" style="font-size: 12px;">上传参考图或工艺单</span><span class="upload-label-sub" style="font-size: 10px;">Max 20MB</span>
                        </div>
                        <input type="file" id="customFile" multiple class="hidden"> 
                        <button type="button" style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; color:#64748b; padding: 4px 12px; font-size:11px; pointer-events:none;">选择文件</button>
                    </div>
                    <div id="customFileList" class="file-list-container" style="max-height: 120px;"></div>
                    
                    <div class="modal-footer" style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 20px; border-top: none;">
                        <button type="button" class="btn-outline" onclick="closeCustomModal()">取消</button>
                        <button type="button" id="saveCustomBtn" onclick="saveCustomization()" style="background:var(--primary-color); color:#fff; border:none; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(170, 0, 0, 0.2);">保存定制需求</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="modal-overlay" id="ndaModal">
        <div class="modal-content modal-md" style="max-width: 580px; padding: 0;">
            <div class="custom-modal-header" style="background: #f8fafc;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-color)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                    商业保密协议
                </h3>
                <button class="modal-close-abs" onclick="closeNdaModal()" style="top:22px; right:25px; background: #fff;">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div class="custom-modal-body" style="padding: 35px 40px; max-height: 60vh; overflow-y: auto;">
                <!-- 极简协议主体 (纯内联样式) -->
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; padding-bottom: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                    
                    <!-- 甲方 -->
                    <div style="flex: 1;">
                        <span style="font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 4px; display: block;">甲方 (披露方 / Disclosing Party)</span>
                        <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b;"><%= user.username %></div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- VS 分隔符 -->
                    <div style="padding: 0 20px; align-self: center; color: #cbd5e1; font-style: italic; font-size: 12px;">VS</div>
                    
                    <!-- 乙方 -->
                    <div style="flex: 1; text-align: right;">
                        <span style="font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 4px; display: block;">乙方 (接收方 / Receiving Party)</span>
                        <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b;">兴城市红绣服饰有限公司</div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>

                <p style="font-size: 13.5px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <strong>第一条 保密内容与范围</strong><br>
                    乙方同意对甲方提供的所有设计稿、图纸、样衣、品牌信息、工艺单及尚未公开的商业计划严格保密。未经甲方明确书面许可，绝不向任何第三方（包括且不限于工厂外包商、竞争对手及公众媒体）透露。
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 13.5px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <strong>第二条 知识产权归属</strong><br>
                    甲方上传的所有设计资料及产生的衍生版型，其全部知识产权及商业版权均完全归甲方所有。乙方仅将上述资料用于甲方指定的产品打样及大货生产环节。
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 13.5px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <strong>第三条 数据销毁与违约责任</strong><br>
                    若双方合作终止，乙方有义务应甲方要求彻底销毁系统内的相关设计数据。如乙方违反上述保密约定，需全额赔偿由此给甲方造成的一切直接商业损失及法务成本。
                </p>
                <div style="background: #fbfcfd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 30px; line-height: 1.6;">
                    * 声明：在您点击“提交定制需求”时，即代表双方自动缔结并生效上述保密条款。<br>
                    * 后续进入大货生产环节前，可根据您的企业合规要求，另行签署具有实体法律效力的纸质版/电子签章版 NDA 协议。
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer" style="padding: 20px 40px 30px; margin-top: 0; border-top: none;">
                <button type="button" style="background:var(--primary-color); color:#fff; border:none; width: 100%; padding: 14px; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(170, 0, 0, 0.15);" onclick="closeNdaModal()">我已了解</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 高清色卡专用纯净预览弹窗 -->
    <div class="modal-overlay" id="swatchFullModal" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95); z-index: 10000; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;">
        <button class="modal-close-abs" onclick="closeSwatchModal()" style="top:20px; right:20px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); color:#fff; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); z-index: 10001;">&times;</button>
        
        <!-- 新增：左切换按钮 -->
        <button id="swatch-prev-btn" onclick="swatchCarouselMove(-1)" style="position: absolute; left: 30px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); z-index: 10005; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); color: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); width: 56px; height: 56px; min-width: 56px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; padding: 0; display: none;">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <!-- 交互容器 -->
        <div id="swatchFullContainer" style="width:100vw; height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; cursor: grab; overflow: hidden;">
            <img id="swatchFullImg" src="" style="user-select: none; -webkit-user-drag: none; transition: transform 0.05s linear; transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1); max-width: 95%; max-height: 95%; object-fit: contain;">
        </div>
    
        <!-- 新增：右切换按钮 -->
        <button id="swatch-next-btn" onclick="swatchCarouselMove(1)" style="position: absolute; right: 30px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); z-index: 10005; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); color: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); width: 56px; height: 56px; min-width: 56px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; padding: 0; display: none;">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline></svg>
        </button>

        <!-- 新增：图片指示器 (1 / 3) -->
        <div id="swatch-counter" style="position: absolute; top: 25px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); color: #fff; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; z-index: 10005; display: none;">1 / 1</div>

        <!-- 操作提示 -->
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 12px; pointer-events: none; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px;">
            滚轮缩放 · 左键拖拽 · 双击重置
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 新增：标签合规性要求参考弹窗 -->
    <div class="modal-overlay" id="labelComplianceModal">
        <div class="modal-content modal-md" style="max-width: 600px;">
            <div class="custom-modal-header" style="background: #fff1f2;">
                <h3 style="color: #e11d48; font-size: 16px; margin: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
                    常见国家服装标签合规要求参考
                </h3>
                <button class="modal-close-abs" onclick="closeLabelComplianceModal()">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div class="custom-modal-body" style="max-height: 60vh; overflow-y: auto; font-size: 12px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6;">
                <p style="margin-top:0; margin-bottom:20px; color:#64748b;">* 以下信息仅供排版参考，不作为最终法律依据。强烈建议您在投产前向当地报关代理确认最新法规。</p>
                
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px; color: #1e293b; font-size: 13px;">🇺🇸 美国 (USA - FTC 要求)</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li><strong>原产地声明</strong> (如: Made in China)，必须位于颈部标签的显著位置。</li>
                        <li><strong>准确的纤维成分及百分比</strong> (按重量递减排列)。</li>
                        <li>制造商的 RN 号或完整公司名称。</li>
                        <li>至少一种推荐的洗涤和保养说明（文字或符合ASTM标准的图标）。</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
    
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px; color: #1e293b; font-size: 13px;">🇪🇺 欧盟 & 🇬🇧 英国</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>使用目标国官方语言表述的纤维成分。</li>
                        <li>必须使用 <strong>ISO/GINETEX 体系标准的洗水符号</strong> (通常5个基本符号按顺序排列：洗涤、漂白、干燥、熨烫、专业纺织品维护)。</li>
                        <li>进口商或制造商在欧盟境内的注册地址。</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
    
                <div style="margin-bottom: 0; padding: 15px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px; color: #1e293b; font-size: 13px;">🇦🇺 澳大利亚 & 新西兰</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>强制使用英文的详细护理说明。</li>
                        <li>原产地标识要求非常严格（必须清晰且独立）。</li>
                        <li>如适用，特定功能性服装（如泳衣、防晒服）需提供 UPF 防晒等级声明。</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 上传进度弹窗 -->
    <div id="uploadModal" style="display:none; position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:10000; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.45); backdrop-filter:blur(4px); align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
        <div style="background:#fff; border-radius:16px; padding:40px 50px; min-width:380px; max-width:440px; text-align:center; box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
            <div id="uploadSpinner" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-color)" stroke-width="2.5" style="animation: rotate 1s linear infinite;">
                    <path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-6.219-8.56"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div id="uploadTitle" style="font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#1e293b; margin-bottom:8px;">正在上传文件...</div>
            <div id="uploadSubtitle" style="font-size:12px; color:#94a3b8; margin-bottom:20px;">请勿关闭页面</div>
            <div style="background:#f1f5f9; border-radius:8px; height:8px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:12px;">
                <div id="uploadProgressBar" style="height:100%; width:0%; background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), #dc2626); border-radius:8px; transition:width 0.3s ease;"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="uploadPercent" style="font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--primary-color);">0%</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- =========================================================================
         核心 JavaScript 逻辑
